) the fine-structure emission lines of OI, SiII, and\nFeII could be 10^2 - 10^3 times stronger than the H2 rotational lines at 28.22\num (J = 2-0) and 17.03 um (J = 3-1).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2005 20:00:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
