rent in the HII regions of distant\ngalaxies hosting intense star formation, and may affect the chemical abundances\nderived from strong-line ratios for such objects (Abridged).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2005 20:17:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
